name: No limitation of provisions by implication
text: §53-39  No limitation of provisions by implication.  No provision in this part applicable specially or only to a redevelopment corporation shall be construed to limit by implication the applicability of this part or any other provision thereof to any other person or corporation. [L 1949, c 379, §23; RL 1955, §143-38; HRS §53-39]
